---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="mt-24 border-t py-16" style="border-color: rgb(var(--line)); background: rgba(var(--surface-2), 0.3);">
  <div class="content-container">
    <div class="grid gap-12 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <a href="/" class="text-xl font-black tracking-tighter" style="font-family: var(--font-display);">
          Signal & Sprocket
        </a>
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-500">
          Astroブログの実装と設計に関するメモを公開している技術ブログです。速さと保守性の両立を目指しています。
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div>
        <h3 class="mb-6 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-400">Content</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm font-medium">
          <li><a href="/blog/" class="text-slate-600 hover:text-brand-600 dark:text-slate-400 dark:hover:text-brand-400 transition-colors">Blog Articles</a></li>
          <li><a href="/blog/page/1/" class="text-slate-600 hover:text-brand-600 dark:text-slate-400 dark:hover:text-brand-400 transition-colors">Archive</a></li>
          <li><a href="/about/" class="text-slate-600 hover:text-brand-600 dark:text-slate-400 dark:hover:text-brand-400 transition-colors">About this site</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="mb-6 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-400">Technical</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm font-medium">
          <li><a href="/rss.xml" class="text-slate-600 hover:text-brand-600 dark:text-slate-400 dark:hover:text-brand-400 transition-colors">RSS Feed</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://astro.build" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-slate-600 hover:text-brand-600 dark:text-slate-400 dark:hover:text-brand-400 transition-colors">Built with Astro</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="mb-6 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-400">Connect</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm font-medium">
          <li><a href="https://github.com/your-username" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-slate-600 hover:text-brand-600 dark:text-slate-400 dark:hover:text-brand-400 transition-colors">GitHub</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://twitter.com/your-username" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-slate-600 hover:text-brand-600 dark:text-slate-400 dark:hover:text-brand-400 transition-colors">Twitter / X</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="mt-16 border-t pt-8 text-center sm:flex sm:items-center sm:justify-between sm:text-left" style="border-color: rgb(var(--line));">
      <p class="text-xs font-medium text-slate-500">
        © {year} Signal & Sprocket. All rights reserved.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-4 flex justify-center gap-6 sm:mt-0">
        <a href="/privacy-policy/" class="text-xs text-slate-400 hover:text-slate-600">Privacy Policy</a>
        <a href="/terms/" class="text-xs text-slate-400 hover:text-slate-600">Terms of Service</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
